Test Case ID: TC-008

Title:
Verify user can log in with valid credentials and pressing the Enter button instead of clicking log in

Preconditions:
1. User is on the Sauce Demo login page.
2. User has a valid username and password.

Test Steps:
1. Enter "standard_user" into the Username field.
2. Enter "secret_sauce" into the Password field.
3. Press the Enter button.

Expected Result:
1. User is successfully authenticated.
2. User is redirected to the Inventory page.
3. Inventory items are displayed.
